objectives: 1   Objectives of zone•  To provide a range of retail, business, entertainment and community uses that serve the needs of people who live in, work in and visit the local area.•  To encourage employment opportunities in accessible locations.•  To maximise public transport patronage and encourage walking and cycling.•  To conserve and enhance the unique sense of place of business centre precincts.•  To ensure that adequate provision is made for infrastructure that supports the viability of business centre precincts.
